    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok i get the science part. what about when things go wrong though? like if someone's dough just comes out looking pale and tasteless or if it burns too fast and tastes bitter—is there a way to explain those failures in terms of the chemical reaction? like is there something that \"disrupts\" it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
